    "Furthermore, journalists possess a recognized professional track record, often with a considerable following, influencing public discourse.",
    "This visibility and credibility they bring to the platform contrast the often covert, manipulative operations of disinformation actors (Molyneux et al. 2020; Wardle and Derakhshan 2017).",
